    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "What about making the hierarchical widgets to have the same classes than the regular one, plus a hierarchical extra class. Something like:\n\n``` css\n<div class=\"ais-menu\">\n  <!-- [...] -->\n  <div class=\"ais-menu-item\">\n    <!-- [...] -->\n  </div>\n  <!-- [...] -->\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"ais-menu ais-hierarchical-menu\">\n  <!-- [...] -->\n  <div class=\"ais-menu-item ais-hierarchical-menu-item\">\n    <!-- [...] -->\n  </div>\n  <!-- [...] -->\n</div>\n```\n",
